These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, collecting
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite
1. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking sprite is the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games |
| Beverage     | sprite    | cola   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk
2 different games are played: go, poker
1. the person playing go is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee        |
| Game      | go  | poker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, house
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee
1. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | house    | ambient |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, taxi
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, mango
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person eating mango is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Transport   | bus      | taxi |
| Food       | broccoli | mango    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, social-worker
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsdahlia is in an even position##4
2. the social-worker is on the right of the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Job           | fisherman | social-worker |
| Flower   | balloon-flower    | dahlia         |

